## Quick Start

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.13+
- [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/getting-started/installation/) installed

### 1. Setup

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

### 2. Install Dependencies

```bash
uv sync
```

### 3. Start the Application

```bash
uv run -m src.api.main
```

The API will be available at:
- API: http://localhost:3000
